{"tid":485280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我本來唔食煙，但今日都買左兩包","createTime":"2017-11-30T23:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T00:41:59.000Z","uid":40470,"like":2074,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"b010165f4ae54f91f71e4bfc87c77a71584ddabf","tid":485280,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"我本來唔食煙，但今日都買左兩包 <br />\n<br />\n買來派比D煙剷食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見佢地咁慘, 加個十幾蚊一包, <br />\n<br />\n就好似殺左佢地老母咁, 鬼殺咁嘈... <br />\n<br />\n我心諗, 唔拎係化, 班煙剷一定好撚窮, <br />\n<br />\n咁拎大個人, 無錢就唔撚好學人食煙啦, 仲要起度鬧政府, <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你無錢食鮑魚咁D鮑魚使唔使減價呀 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n咁我就做下好心, 買左兩包煙派比街邊D煙剷, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD 煙剷個撚個都狗衝埋來拎免費煙... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇見佢地個樣就好笑, 成個乞兒咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就用左二百蚊都唔使, <br />\n<br />\n就見到成班煙剷好似乞兒咁寒寒酸酸問我拎煙食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地拎到支煙之後好撚開心, 即刻堆埋垃圾筒傍邊開餐... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乞兒真係乞兒, 有野食都要起垃圾筒傍邊食....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我下次買多幾包煙派比煙剷, 再享受做善長既樂趣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e631dae791f0d7f9b33d1655fc9452fae2d89d9","tid":485280,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f32d033057e6df43fe6611dfe275ec015f92002","tid":485280,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee99e5b156d1852f45f26811f07f6aef3baa984","tid":485280,"uid":142706,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:57:47.000Z","msg":"正評上一頁"},{"pid":"631425605d154df6c2d32bdd41b1cd6867d925cd","tid":485280,"uid":106847,"like":950,"dislike":8,"score":942,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"真心想講食唔緊要<br />\n但可唔可以咪撚一路行一路食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知唔知你強迫緊後面啲人食晒你啲二手煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仆你個街"},{"pid":"8300afd1cfaf34ee4c6b4a2f7101352868ce9dd2","tid":485280,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe5e49f803a58c30e4787ac7d382dda19dcbcae","tid":485280,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"無人反駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7715537eaec39cd05a086c0fe7d6bb1640a856","tid":485280,"uid":94452,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人反駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaf001ee4683066b89c8810147285d710459488","tid":485280,"uid":139139,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:01:42.000Z","msg":"買得兩包，如果真係食煙<br />\n日日都食兩包啦，一個月食咗半份糧"},{"pid":"04848a9780899caeb5dd1d187157cc278db134c7","tid":485280,"uid":45028,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:01:51.000Z","msg":"反咩駁<br />\n比著我食煙嘅話<br />\n都好似啲死煙鏟咁等樓豬請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdab6851091af7429c505a98f1696785481e91f","tid":485280,"uid":673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"有冇影相<br />\n想睇下班乞衣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e7f775fedf8